This is a script to automate the initial installation and configuration of my devices.

Simply run 'Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bruno-fct/MyRig-setup/main/choco-install.ps1'))' on PowerShell.
